# …except the desktop UI bundle the daemon serves. It ships via git → pipx
# (there's no node build step at install time), so the built SPA MUST be
# committed or the local daemon serves a stale/empty UI. Rebuild with
# `pnpm --dir src/dispatch/web/desktop build` and commit the result.
!/src/dispatch/web/desktop/dist/
!/src/dispatch/web/desktop/dist/**
